name: Temple House Practice
directions: From the front entrance turn right, from the back turn left and walk past reception. It's just opposite the waiting room and just before the double doors is a small corridor to the right. First door on the right. Ask staff if confused.
comment: Unisex bathroom for all. Can't remember if it has a changing table.

name: Starbucks
directions: Wall opposite entrance doors, barista counter on your left, restrooms to your right.
comment: Two single toilet bathrooms with door codes. Get the door code from a barista. I don't think you have to be a paying customer. Ask for an ice water if you need a reason to be in the shop.

name: Joshua Tree Saloon
comment: The town is small and chill enough that they probably won’t mind if you use the restroom without ordering
